<thetext>Description of problem: dnf dumps core if it gets an invalid rpm archive. Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): dnf-1.1.10-6.fc25.noarch How reproducible: $ rm -f thunderbird-52.0-2.fc25.x86_64.rpm $ touch
thunderbird-52.0-2.fc25.x86_64.rpm $ dnf update thunderbird-52.0-2.fc25.x86_64.rpm Last metadata expiration check: 0:27:00 ago on Mon Apr 17 16:01:57 2017. Segmentation fault (core dumped) $ echo Hallo &gt; thunderbird-52.0-2.fc25.x86_64.rpm Last
metadata expiration check: 0:27:10 ago on Mon Apr 17 16:01:57 2017. Segmentation fault (core dumped) Actual results: core dump Expected results: error message &quot;Invalid/Broken RPM archive&quot; Corinna</thetext>
</long_desc>
